      "text": "{user}さん……\nどう？　似合ってるかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…\nHow do I look?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.2853741776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、とても似合ってるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ you look amazing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.8999999523,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.4666658561
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、そっかそっかー！\nそんなに似合ってるんだー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ really?\nI look that good?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "……そっか、そっか。えへへ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I see‚ I see. Hehe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.4999998252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.9333331585
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんも着替えたんだね\n……タキシードに！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ you changed too.\n…Into a tuxedo!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ドレスを選んだ時、意味深に笑ってたのはこのことか\nいきなり着替えるよう言われて驚いたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You laughed mysteriously when choosing a dress. Is this why?\nI was surprised when you suddenly asked me to change.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.8666684469,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.7666682721
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "うんうん、とっても似合ってる。キリッ！　って感じ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ yeah‚ you look really good. Sharp!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.7666682721,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "大体なんで俺がタキシードを着る必要があるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why do I need to wear a tuxedo?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.6666682721,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.8333349388
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくのウエディングドレスでしょ？\nだから、二人で撮った方が楽しいかなって！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a special wedding dress that we prepared‚ right?\nSo‚ it's more fun to take pictures together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.5727823675,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.9000016054
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "お店の人も「ぜひお二人で！ その方が参考になります\nし！ 店内掲示しませんから！」って言ってたでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Plus‚ the store clerk said‚ \"Please take photos together!\nIt'll be more helpful. We won't display them in the store!\" right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.8688677152,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あそこまで熱心に言われたら、断るに断れないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When they say it so earnestly‚ I can't refuse.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.3333349388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.1000038942
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "念のためもう一回言っておくが、これはあくまで芽衣の\nお父さんのためだからな。絶対みんなには言うなよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just to be clear‚ this is all for your dad.\nDon't tell anyone‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.8000017803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "はーい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.3333372276,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.8333372276
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "あ、寝ぐせ寝ぐせ。ほら、こっち来て？　直すから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ your hair is messy. Come here? Let me do it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.8333372276,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あ、おい……スタッフの方が見てるだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-hey… Staff are watching.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.0666705609,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "これくらい平気平気\nはい、これでばっちり！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's fine‚ it's fine.\nThere‚ all set!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.2666684469,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.5000038942
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても……ドレス姿の撮影だけでも\nこんなに一杯準備するんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… Even just for dress photoshoots‚\nthere's so much preparation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.5333351136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "結婚式の準備は、きっともっと大変なんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Planning a wedding must be even more hectic‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.300006946,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.6666736127
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。友人の招待もあるし、二次会も開くし……\n相当大変だと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ probably. Inviting friends‚ holding a reception…\nIt must be quite stressful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.8778130532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.100006946
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "でもさ、それだけ頑張って式を挙げるからこそ\n一生の思い出になるんじゃないかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you know‚ because they put so much effort into it‚\nit becomes a lifelong memory.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.5000017803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.700006946
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣もね、月ストのみんなと一杯練習して、頑張って\n準備するから、どのライブも思い出に残ってるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just like how every live performance with Moon Tempest\nbecomes a cherished memory because we practice so hard and do our best.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.4000017803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "頑張った分だけ記憶に残る……か\n確かに、その感覚は分かるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The harder you work‚ the more it sticks in your memory…\nI get that feeling‚ definitely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.0333351136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.100006946
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "結婚かぁ……考えてみると凄いよね\n誰かと何十年も一緒に暮らすんだよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Marriage… it's amazing when you think about it‚ huh?\nSpending decades with someone‚ no matter where you are?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.4000017803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03-mei016.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣が結婚するなら、家にいても、出かけても\nずっと楽しく一緒にいられる人がいいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If Mei were to get married‚ I'd want someone\nwho I can have fun with whether we're at home or out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.5000017803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.8666736127
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_07_03-mei017.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば……芽衣、{user}さんと\nいると、どこで何してても楽しいよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of which… When Mei is with you‚ {user}-san‚\nno matter where or what we're doing‚ it's always fun!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.4429127085,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
